=== cold_call.glp ===
Cold call befriending protocol.
Goal: social_graph(Id, [msg(user, Id, connect(Target))|In], Fs)

Four phases:
1. User initiation: connect(Target) request
2. Offer transmission: intro(Id, Id, Resp) sent
3. User consultation: befriend(From, Resp) shown
4. Channel establishment: response processed

Uses inject/4 to defer insertion until response bound.
